ort(xuất&nbsp;HDMi), Vga out, Lan, SD, SC PCi, Wifi chuẩn N,<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Sạc zin, Pin&nbsp;zin 6&nbsp;cell, 9 cell</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Win7 pro theo m&aacute;y, c&oacute; thể&nbsp;c&agrave;i Win 10 bản quyền nh</p>','',105,1,47,'2018-03-08 08:07:46','2018-04-17 10:15:57');
